{"tid":727441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想死 你問我答","createTime":"2018-07-03T04:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T16:51:21.000Z","uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"590453de8e6b35771dde6865540bdb9a26bfc6cf","tid":727441,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bcf2199f0c15465a2926cdd0d89dad26bcf35d","tid":727441,"uid":60066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"點解？"},{"pid":"26cb48700cffb887d08d21344061567ea9d94fc0","tid":727441,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"0d0c0d7066af2c64fac3cc7cb7693ab83d3d7c74","tid":727441,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"想點死？"},{"pid":"89def342cf45392c0493c438126a33dd7e57ed3f","tid":727441,"uid":190969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"點解香港冇安樂死"},{"pid":"5becbe715ec37e00e5e762658d88af130303f4d2","tid":727441,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:40:33.000Z","msg":"做人無動力 玩完"},{"pid":"05433a71e2e35c4dd4bd0aa499b9854a2af2a01c","tid":727441,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=wWJOMiaAdzgtWeCRBVsiuv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=57e35971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『真心話室』（星期一至日，下午８時至凌晨１時）即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"a073ed2ade9b95ad42920ca837c169d39ccce65e","tid":727441,"uid":177004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"點睇「寵物小精靈」改名做「精靈寶可夢」？"},{"pid":"426e9fc7dc83e5f579528092c03614a17dd829e0","tid":727441,"uid":177004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"家中有何人？<br />\n關係如何？"}]}